nt/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sampha（左）的三张并排图片，所有内容都记录下来（中心）和佛罗伦萨·韦尔奇（Florence Welch）（右）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/EverythingIsRecordedNeverFelt-Better-single-Florence-Welch-Sampha-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/everything-is-recorded">录制的一切都</a>分享了一张新单曲，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">佛罗伦萨·韦尔奇（Florence Welch）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">桑帕（Sampha）</a> - 在下面听“从未感觉更好”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/florence-the-machine-dance-fever-3223402">佛罗伦萨 +机器 - “舞蹈发烧”评论：歌手重生的胜利声</a></strong></li></ul><p>幸福的曲目将出现在第三张录音室专辑中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/richard-russell">。</a>标题为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/richard-russell-launches-new-everything-is-recorded-compilation-temporary-3814374">“临时”</a> ，该记录将于本周五（2月28日）通过XL（<a href="https://everythingisrecorded.x-l.co/temporary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）发布。</p><p> “从来没有感觉更好”被描述为“超然，赞美诗的音乐”，并伴随着克里斯蒂安·梅尔卡多（Kristian Mercado）和梅拉（Mela）谋杀案的官方音乐录影带。 Sampha和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence +机器</a>主人都为这首歌贡献了人声。</p><p>在这里调整： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="一切都记录了 - 从来没有感觉更好（英尺。佛罗伦萨·韦尔奇和桑帕）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HRz_C1LVhCU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>从前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-cyrus">“</a>临时”单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bill-callahan">“</a>豪猪纹身”（壮举。 ＃3&#39;（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">壮举</a>。</p><p>录制的一切都将庆祝专辑的发行，并在明天和星期五晚上（2月27日28日28日在伦敦的另一个世界上售罄的“临时：太空”现场活动。 <a href="https://dice.fm/event/wwav9x-everything-is-recorded-presents-temporary-space-27th-feb-anotherland-london-tickets?lng=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到更多信息</a>。</p><p> LP的其他贡献者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/berwyn">Berwyn</a> ，Alabaster Deplume， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kamasi-washington">Kamasi Washington</a> ，Rickey Washington，Roses Gabor， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-penate">JackPeéate</a> ，Samantha Morton，以及时间滋养（请参阅下面的曲目列表）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814377" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814377" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814377" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Everything-Is-Recorded-Temporary-LP-artwork.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" alt="记录了“临时” LP艺术品" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Everything-Is-Recorded-Temporary-LP-artwork.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Everything-Is-Recorded-Temporary-LP-artwork.-CREDIT_-Press-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Everything-Is-Recorded-Temporary-LP-artwork.-CREDIT_-Press-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Everything-Is-Recorded-Temporary-LP-artwork.-CREDIT_-P