t-3838497">Gyubin策划了名为“我们的播放列表”的<em>NME</em>爱情歌曲的独家播放列表，</a>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bee-gees">Bee Gees</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-newton-john">Olivia Newton-John</a>等永恒的经典作品，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a>的新浪漫片， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">Ed Ed Sheeran</a>的最爱还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">K-Pop</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iu">IU</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gyubin-music-video-new-single-like-u-100-3841342">Gyubin帖子丢弃了新单曲“像U 100”的嬉戏音乐视频，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
